# LINE BK Assignment

## Database Schema

The database consists of several tables:

- `users`: Stores basic user information
- `user_greetings`: Contains personalized greetings for users
- `accounts`: Main account information
- `account_balances`: Tracks account monetary balances
- `account_details`: Additional account properties
- `account_flags`: Stores various account flags/settings
- `transactions`: Records transaction history
- `debit_cards`: Basic debit card information
- `debit_card_status`: Tracks card status
- `debit_card_details`: Additional card properties
- `debit_card_design`: Card design/appearance settings
- `banners`: Marketing/promotional banners

